OL,3,CSteve Backshall's wildlife threat
OL,4,Cwarning as shark washes up in Jersey
OL,6,FWildlife presenter Steve Backshall
OL,7,Fsays sharks in waters around Britain
OL,8,Fare under "enormous threat" after an
OL,9,Fendangered species washed up on a
OL,10,FJersey beach.
OL,12,FOn Sunday 7 June, a Smalltooth sand
OL,13,Ftiger shark was reported as stranded
OL,14,Fat Greve d'Azette.
OL,16,FThis type of shark has never been
OL,17,Ffound in Jersey before, according to
OL,18,Fofficial records.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
