PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781470067
OL,3,CSteve Backshall's wildlife threat
OL,4,Cwarning as shark washes up in Jersey
OL,6,F"There was a Great White spotted in
OL,7,Fthe Mediterranean and filmed, and a
OL,8,FSmalltooth sand tiger swept up on a
OL,9,Fbeach in the Channel Islands, which is
OL,10,Fincredibly rare."
OL,12,F"I think it's focusing our attention
OL,13,Fon what is in our seas. Here in the
OL,14,FUK, we have at least 45 different
OL,15,Fkinds of sharks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1781470067
OL,3,CSteve Backshall's wildlife threat
OL,4,Cwarning as shark washes up in Jersey
OL,6,F"But there are also sharks, like the
OL,7,FSmalltooth sand tiger shark, that
OL,8,Foccasionally wash up on our shores -
OL,9,FHammerheads, Greenland sharks... that
OL,10,Fmay be incredibly rare, but they are
OL,11,Foccasionally out there.
OL,13,F"So we have an astounding shark fauna
OL,14,Fin our seas. It's very little
OL,15,Funderstood and it is under enormous
OL,16,Fthreat."
OL,18,FBiologists have suggested warmer seas
OL,19,Fcould be to blame for it ending up on
OL,20,Fa Jersey beach.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
